<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Código de Verificação - SkillConnect</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
            .email-container {
                width: 100% !important;
                min-width: 100% !important;
            }
            .mobile-padding {
                padding: 20px !important;
            }
            .code-text {
                font-size: 32px !important;
                letter-spacing: 6px !important;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 24px !important;
            }
            h2 {
                font-size: 20px !important;
            }
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .code-text {
                font-size: 28px !important;
                letter-spacing: 4px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; min-width: 100%; width: 100%;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 20px;">
                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" class="email-container" style="max-width: 520px; width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff;">
                    
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="padding: 0 0 48px 0;">
                            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="18" stroke="#27ae60" stroke-width="2"/>
                                <path d="M14 20L18 24L26 16" stroke="#27ae60" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                            </svg>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="padding: 0 40px;">
                            
                            <div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
                                <svg width="56" height="56" viewBox="0 0 56 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                    <rect x="8" y="16" width="40" height="28" rx="2" stroke="#27ae60" stroke-width="2"/>
                                    <path d="M8 20H48" stroke="#27ae60" stroke-width="2"/>
                                    <circle cx="20" cy="32" r="2" fill="#27ae60"/>
                                    <circle cx="28" cy="32" r="2" fill="#27ae60"/>
                                    <circle cx="36" cy="32" r="2" fill="#27ae60"/>
                                </svg>
                            </div>

                            <h1 style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2;">Código de Verificação</h1>
                            
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 40px 0; color: #666666; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 400;">
                                Use o código abaixo para recuperar sua senha e acessar sua conta com segurança.
                            </p>

                            <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px 24px; margin-bottom: 40px; border: 1px solid #e8e8e8;">
                                <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #999999; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 600;">Seu Código</p>
                                <p class="code-text" style="margin: 0; color: #27ae60; font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 8px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">{{verificationCode}}</p>
                            </div>

                            <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 40px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td align="center" style="padding: 0 12px;">
                                        <div style="text-align: center;">
                                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
                                                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="#27ae60" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                                                <path d="M12 6V12L16 14" stroke="#27ae60" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                                            </svg>
                                            <p style="margin: 0 0 4px 0; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;">Válido por 10 minutos</p>
                                            <p style="margin: 0; color: #999999; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;">Código de uso único</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>

                            <div style="background-color: #f0faf9; border-left: 3px solid #27ae60; padding: 16px 20px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: left;">
                                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="width: 100%;">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td style="padding-right: 12px; vertical-align: top; width: 20px;">
                                            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                                <path d="M10 2C5.58 2 2 5.58 2 10C2 14.42 5.58 18 10 18C14.42 18 18 14.42 18 10C18 5.58 14.42 2 10 2ZM10 16C6.69 16 4 13.31 4 10C4 6.69 6.69 4 10 4C13.31 4 16 6.69 16 10C16 13.31 13.31 16 10 16Z" fill="#27ae60"/>
                                                <path d="M9 13H11V15H9V13Z" fill="#27ae60"/>
                                                <path d="M9 5H11V11H9V5Z" fill="#27ae60"/>
                                            </svg>
                                        </td>
                                        <td style="vertical-align: top;">
                                            <p style="margin: 0; color: #1e8449; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 500;">
                                                <strong>Dica de Segurança:</strong> Nunca compartilhe este código. A SkillConnect jamais solicitará este código por telefone.
                                            </p>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </div>

                            <p style="margin: 0 0 48px 0; color: #999999; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 400;">
                                Se você não solicitou esta recuperação de senha, ignore este email. Sua conta permanecerá segura.
                            </p>

                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="height: 1px; background-color: #e8e8e8; margin: 0 40px;"></td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="padding: 32px 40px;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">
                                SkillConnect
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #999999; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400;">
                                © {{year}} SkillConnect. Todos os direitos reservados.
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0; color: #cccccc; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 400;">
                                Este é um email automático. Por favor, não responda.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
